<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>VYOM VOID — Full Brand Identity Guide</title>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --void-black: #0A0A0F;
      --deep-space: #1A1A2E;
      --cosmic-navy: #16213E;
      --nebula-purple: #7B2FBE;
      --vyom-cyan: #00D4FF;
      --stardust: #E8E8F0;
      --supernova-red: #FF3864;
      --muted: #888899;
      --border: rgba(232, 232, 240, 0.08);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--void-black);
      color: var(--stardust);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 40px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 72px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -3px;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: var(--stardust);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--vyom-cyan);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--stardust);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    h4 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      color: #B0B0C0;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    section:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--nebula-purple);
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .divider-line {
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--nebula-purple);
      margin: 30px auto;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--deep-space);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card-dark {
      background: #0D0D18;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .grid-4 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .swatch {
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px 14px 14px;
    }

    .swatch-name {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .swatch-hex {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .swatch-role {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 4px 4px 4px 0;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .tag-accent {
      border-color: var(--nebula-purple);
      color: var(--nebula-purple);
    }

    .tag-cyan {
      border-color: var(--vyom-cyan);
      color: var(--vyom-cyan);
    }

    blockquote {
      border-left: 2px solid var(--nebula-purple);
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--stardust);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .logo-preview {
      background: #111120;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      min-height: 160px;
    }

    .logo-wordmark {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: var(--stardust);
    }

    .logo-sub {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    th {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    }

    td {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: #B0B0C0;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .collection-num {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--nebula-purple);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .collection-title {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--stardust);
      margin: 4px 0;
    }

    .collection-meaning {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--vyom-cyan);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .website-section {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .website-section:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .ws-num {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--border);
      min-width: 50px;
    }

    .ws-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--stardust);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .ws-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: var(--vyom-cyan);
    }

    .highlight-purple {
      color: var(--nebula-purple);
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 10px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(123, 47, 190, 0.2);
      color: var(--nebula-purple);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123, 47, 190, 0.3);
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .font-preview {
      padding: 16px 20px;
      background: #0D0D18;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .font-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    ul li {
      color: #B0B0C0;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .print-note {
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .page-break {
      page-break-before: always;
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        background: white;
        color: #111;
      }

      .card,
      .card-dark {
        background: #f5f5f5;
        border-color: #ddd;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge">Brand Identity Document v1.0</div>
      <h1>VYOM<br><span>VOID</span></h1>
      <div class="divider-line"></div>
      <p class="hero-tagline">Where the sky meets nothingness</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">Indian Gen Z</span>
        <span class="tag tag-cyan">Print on demand</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">Dark theme</span>
        <span class="tag tag-cyan">Sanskrit roots</span>
        <span class="tag">Streetwear</span>
        <span class="tag">Cosmic / space</span>
      </div>
      <div
        style="margin-top: 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--nebula-purple);">
            vyomvoid.com</div>
          <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);">.com available</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">
            vyomvoid.in</div>
          <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);">.in available</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--stardust);">
            @vyomvoid</div>
          <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);">Instagram handle</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BRAND STORY -->
    <section>
      <h2>01 — Brand story</h2>
      <h3>The origin of VYOM VOID</h3>
      <p><strong style="color:var(--stardust);">Vyom</strong> (व्योम) is a Sanskrit word meaning <em>sky</em> or
        <em>space</em> — infinite, ancient, and sacred in Indian culture. <strong
          style="color:var(--stardust);">Void</strong> is the modern English expression of nothingness — dark,
        boundless, and alive with tension.</p>
      <p>VYOM VOID is the collision of these two worlds. It is a brand born from the intersection of ancient Indian
        cosmic philosophy and the raw, restless energy of modern Gen Z culture. Every piece of clothing we make is a
        portal — between the seen and the unseen, between earth and infinity.</p>
      <p>We are not just a t-shirt brand. We are a frequency. A signal from the void.</p>
      <blockquote>"The universe was born from shunya — nothingness. So were we."</blockquote>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Mission</h4>
          <p>To create wearable art for the generation that exists between worlds — digitally native, culturally rooted,
            and unafraid of the dark.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Vision</h4>
          <p>To become India's most iconic dark-aesthetic streetwear brand — recognized globally as the brand that gave
            the cosmos a voice in fashion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TARGET AUDIENCE -->
    <section>
      <h2>02 — Target audience</h2>
      <h3>Who wears VYOM VOID</h3>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Age</h4>
          <p
            style="font-size: 28px; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; color: var(--nebula-purple); margin: 0;">
            16 — 26</p>
          <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 6px;">Indian Gen Z and young millennials</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Gender</h4>
          <p style="font-size: 14px;">Unisex / gender-neutral. Oversized fits appeal to all.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Geography</h4>
          <p style="font-size: 14px;">Tier 1 + Tier 2 India first. Global Indian diaspora second.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <h4>Psychographics</h4>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px;">
          <span class="tag tag-accent">Dark aesthetic lovers</span>
          <span class="tag tag-accent">Anime culture</span>
          <span class="tag tag-accent">Space + cosmos fans</span>
          <span class="tag">Sanskrit / mythology interest</span>
          <span class="tag">Instagram aesthetics</span>
          <span class="tag">Limited drop culture</span>
          <span class="tag">Anti-fast-fashion</span>
          <span class="tag">Music festival crowd</span>
          <span class="tag">Gamers + streamers</span>
          <span class="tag">College students</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Customer persona</h4>
        <p><strong style="color:var(--stardust);">Arjun, 19, Pune.</strong> He's a design student who listens to lo-fi
          hip-hop and watches anime at 2am. His wardrobe is 80% black. He discovers brands through Instagram Reels and
          Reddit. He buys limited drops to feel exclusive, not mass-market. He respects Indian culture but hates
          clichés. He wants something that feels like it was made for him — dark, cosmic, meaningful.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BRAND PERSONALITY -->
    <section>
      <h2>03 — Brand personality & voice</h2>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div>
          <h3>Personality</h3>
          <div class="card">
            <table>
              <tr>
                <td style="color: var(--vyom-cyan); width: 40%;">Tone</td>
                <td>Dark, poetic, confident, slightly mysterious</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="color: var(--vyom-cyan);">Archetype</td>
                <td>The Outlaw meets The Sage</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="color: var(--vyom-cyan);">Energy</td>
                <td>Quiet intensity — not aggressive, but unflinching</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="color: var(--vyom-cyan);">Vibe</td>
                <td>Like the universe at 3am — vast, dark, beautiful</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Voice examples</h3>
          <div class="card">
            <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 8px;"><span style="color:var(--muted);">Caption
                style:</span><br>"Born in the gap between stars and silence. Drop 002 — NAKSHATRA."</p>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 8px;"><span style="color:var(--muted);">Product
                description:</span><br>"You are made of the same matter as everything that has ever burned out and
              disappeared. Wear it."</p>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;"><span style="color:var(--muted);">CTA text:</span><br>"Enter
              the void →" / "Claim your frequency" / "Drop into the cosmos"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>We are</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Poetic and dark</li>
            <li>Culturally proud (Indian roots)</li>
            <li>Exclusive and drop-driven</li>
            <li>Minimalist in copy, bold in design</li>
            <li>Cosmic and philosophical</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h4>We are NOT</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Loud or aggressive</li>
            <li>Preachy about Indian culture</li>
            <li>Generic "galaxy print" brands</li>
            <li>Overly discounted / sale-heavy</li>
            <li>Following trends blindly</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COLOR PALETTE -->
    <section>
      <h2>04 — Color palette</h2>
      <h3>The void spectrum</h3>
      <div
        style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(110px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#0A0A0F;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#E8E8F0;">Void black</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#888;">#0A0A0F</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#555;">Primary bg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#1A1A2E;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#E8E8F0;">Deep space</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#888;">#1A1A2E</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#555;">Card bg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#16213E;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#E8E8F0;">Cosmic navy</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#888;">#16213E</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#555;">Section bg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#7B2FBE;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#F0E0FF;">Nebula purple</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#ddc;">#7B2FBE</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#ddc;">Brand accent</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#00D4FF;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#001F33;">Vyom cyan</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#003;">#00D4FF</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#004;">Links / glow</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#E8E8F0;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#1A1A2E;">Stardust</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#555;">#E8E8F0</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#777;">Primary text</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swatch" style="background:#FF3864;">
          <div class="swatch-name" style="color:#fff;">Supernova</div>
          <div class="swatch-hex" style="color:#ffd;">#FF3864</div>
          <div class="swatch-role" style="color:#ffd;">Alert / sale</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Color usage rules</h4>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Element</th>
            <th>Color</th>
            <th>Hex</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Website background</td>
            <td>Void black</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#0A0A0F</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Card / panel backgrounds</td>
            <td>Deep space</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#1A1A2E</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Primary headings</td>
            <td>Stardust</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#E8E8F0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Body text</td>
            <td>Muted stardust</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#B0B0C0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Brand accent / CTA buttons</td>
            <td>Nebula purple</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#7B2FBE</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Links / secondary accent</td>
            <td>Vyom cyan</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#00D4FF</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Sale tags / urgency</td>
            <td>Supernova red</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#FF3864</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>T-shirt base color</td>
            <td>Black / Charcoal</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace; color: var(--vyom-cyan);">#0D0D0D / #1C1C1C</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TYPOGRAPHY -->
    <section>
      <h2>05 — Typography system</h2>
      <h3>Font stack</h3>
      <div class="font-preview">
        <div
          style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--stardust); letter-spacing: -2px; line-height: 1;">
          VYOM VOID</div>
        <div class="font-label">Display / Logo — Syne 800 · Use for: brand name, hero text, drop titles, large numerals
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="font-preview">
        <div
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--stardust);">
          Enter the void. Wear the cosmos.</div>
        <div class="font-label">Heading — Space Grotesk 500 · Use for: section headings, product names, nav items</div>
      </div>
      <div class="font-preview">
        <div style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #B0B0C0; line-height: 1.8;">Vyom Void is
          not just a brand. It is a frequency born from the Sanskrit cosmos, forged in dark space, and worn by those who
          feel at home in the dark.</div>
        <div class="font-label">Body — DM Sans 400 · Use for: product descriptions, about page, blog</div>
      </div>
      <div class="font-preview">
        <div
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);">
          WHERE SKY MEETS NOTHINGNESS · DROP 001</div>
        <div class="font-label">Label / caption — Space Grotesk 500, uppercase, tracked · Use for: section labels,
          product tags, drop numbering</div>
      </div>
      <div class="print-note">
        <strong style="color: var(--vyom-cyan);">Google Fonts URLs:</strong><br>
        Syne: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Syne<br>
        Space Grotesk: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Space+Grotesk<br>
        DM Sans: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/DM+Sans<br><br>
        <strong style="color: var(--vyom-cyan);">Fallback alternative:</strong> Bebas Neue (display) + Inter (body) for
        print/offline use.
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LOGO -->
    <section>
